18774683466 Deposited a new message:
"Hello, I'm calling on behalf of National General Insurance, an Allstate company. We appreciate your business. However, we recently sent you paperwork outlining items that must be returned in order for us to process your policy and maintain the competitive rates. If you have already submitted the requested items, you may disregard this message. If you have any questions, please press one to be connected with a customer service representative. Thank you for your continued business."
